e World Championships in Zhengzhou, central China's Henan Province, to compete with the world's top modern pentathletes.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhengzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5042128652282999e-16, \"text\": \"Zhengzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhengzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhengzhou\"}, {\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9248907832638977, \"rank\": 0.07576370998203763, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Henan Province\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mid\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's top modern pentathletes\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since I was already qualified for the Olympics, I considered the World Championships an opportunity to test myself, to see how I perform in a noisy environment in front of crowd,\\\" Zhang said.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"a noisy environment\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"crowd\", \"from\": 1356, \"t