edia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sprinting\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"my weakness\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"recent months\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I surpassed an opponent, I wanted to know by how much I did it and if she was close to catching up with me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opponent\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about her goal for Paris Olympics, Zhang said that she wants to do her best, and, if possible, surpass her regular best.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her goal\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLOAD\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation 